                <h1>Exploring the Surreal Genius of Salvador Dalí</h1>
                <p>Salvador Dalí, a prominent figure of the Surrealist movement, is renowned for his dreamlike artworks and eccentric persona. His masterpieces, like "The Persistence of Memory," blend reality with fantasy, evoking deep emotions and challenging perceptions. Dalí's innovative techniques and bold imagination make him a timeless icon of art.</p>
